sub_title: Resident doctor in the Netherlands, specializing in Geriatric Medicine
summary:
Highly motivated Dutch resident doctor with currently four years of work experience in Internal Medicine and Geriatrics. Currently in the third year of a five-year program specializing in Geriatric Medicine. 
I'm currently looking for a work experience / residency in the UK or Ireland in palliative medicine. I'm very keen to experience the care for frail and elderly patients from another perspective. An international work experience will surely teach me new skills and bring new ideas, while allowing me to apply what I know in another setting. 
Currently living together with my partner, who works in IT, in Utrecht, the Netherlands.
